title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Fantasy 5' game
maintext:
SACRAMENTO (AP) _ The winning numbers in Monday evening’s drawing of the California Lottery’s “Fantasy 5” game were:
17-26-29-30-31
(seventeen, twenty-six, twenty-nine, thirty, thirty-one)
Estimated jackpot: $67,000
¶ The numbers are listed in sequential order, but any combination wins.
